reviewText:
WSU is a amazing woman's pro wrestling promotion
all these woman can work better then some men
These girls ain't Divas or Knockouts there pure athletes that work stiff, take crazy bumps and high spots

This is a promotion that is clawing and scratching to keep wrestling in Pro Wrestling not Sports Entertainment
It's a promotion made for fans that want good wrestling in there show

It's very hard to try and sell wrestling in 2015 let alone woman's wrestling but, this product will blow you away
It's truly one of the best kept secrets in all North American pro wrestling
Check out there stuff on youtube and prove me wrong
